messages.message:
Sr Java Developer Needed in Tempe

In reading your profile I thought I would reach out to you in regards to a Sr. Java Developer Role I am working on in Tempe AZ. 

I am seeking a SR. Dev with knowledge of Java, and Object Oriented Design
( Spring and Java EE) Java concurrency and relational databases are required, Experiience with AWS facilites such as EC2, S3, and RDS would be a huge +

In addition to the above we need someone that isnt afraid to tell us their ideas and suggest new applications. You should be able to work alone with little supervision but you must also be able to be part of a team and work together as well. The workpolace is very unique and supportive. The workplace is also a very flexable working environment. 

reach out to me via my email mscornavacco@teemagroup.com or reply to this message with your resume and phone number so we can chat about what it will take for you to make a move.

Mike Scornavacco
Anytime are you interested in speaking about the position?
